            <p class="eyebrow6">Our Story</p>
            <h2 class="h6" id="story-h2">We didn't study cleaning.<br /><span class="ac">We lived it.</span></h2>
            <p>When Pau and Stefania landed in Melbourne, they weren't thinking about starting a business. They were thinking about building a life in a new country — and that meant getting to work. Like a lot of new arrivals, cleaning was where they started.</p>
            <p>What surprised them wasn't the work itself. It was how much room there was to do it better. Poor communication. Inconsistent results. Cleaners who showed up late, or used whatever products were on hand. Clients who never knew what to expect. The industry wasn't bad — it was just stuck.</p>
