              <p>The standard we set for ourselves wasn't "good enough for a cleaner." It was: would we be happy coming home to this?</p>
            </div>
            <p>In 2017 they started going directly to clients. No agency, no middleman — just Pau and Stefania showing up consistently, doing exactly what they said they would, and asking for honest feedback. The reputation they built was slow, earned, and real.</p>
